				{
					"attributes" : 
					{
						"documentation" : "Swap return, which transfers the crypto asset back to the pool and removes the swap from\r\nthe active swap mapping. Can be called by the pool or the swap's oracle, but only if the\r\nescrow lock time expired.\r\n\n     * Emits a `Returned` or `PoolReturned` event with the swap's hash.\r",
