					"attributes" : 
					{
						"documentation" : "Given all valid swap details, returns its status. The return can be:\r\n0: the swap details are invalid, swap doesn't exist, or was already released/returned.\r\n>1: the swap was created, and the value is a timestamp indicating end of its lock time.\r",
